msgid "### KV Pool Parameter Description"
msgstr "### KV池参数说明"

msgid "#### `kv_load_failure_policy`: KV Load Failure Handling Policy"
msgstr "#### `kv_load_failure_policy`：KV加载失败处理策略"

msgid "`kv_load_failure_policy` is a top-level field in `kv-transfer-config`."
msgstr "`kv_load_failure_policy` 是 `kv-transfer-config` 中的顶级字段。"

msgid ""
"* `recompute`: When KV loading fails, vLLM rolls the request back to the last valid prefix and reschedules it to recompute the failed KV blocks. Hybrid attention models (e.g. DeepSeekV4, Qwen 3.5) are not supported yet.\n"
"* `fail`: When KV loading fails, the affected request is terminated directly with an error."
msgstr ""
"* `recompute`：当KV加载失败时，vLLM将请求回滚到最后一个有效前缀，并重新调度以重新计算失败的KV块。尚不支持混合注意力模型（例如DeepSeekV4、Qwen 3.5）。\n"
"* `fail`：当KV加载失败时，受影响的请求将直接终止并返回错误。"

msgid ""
"The default value in vLLM is `fail`. If you want the request to fall back to"
" recomputation after a KV load failure, set it to `recompute`."
msgstr "vLLM中的默认值为 `fail`。如果希望在KV加载失败后请求回退到重新计算，请将其设置为 `recompute`。"

msgid ""
"When `MultiConnector` is used, configure `kv_load_failure_policy` on the "
"`MultiConnector` top-level `kv-transfer-config` instead of the child "
"connectors."
msgstr ""
"使用 `MultiConnector` 时，请在 `MultiConnector` 顶级 `kv-transfer-config` 上配置 "
"`kv_load_failure_policy`，而不是在子连接器上配置。"

msgid ""
"#### `kv_connector_extra_config`: Additional Configurable Parameters for "
"Pooling"
msgstr "#### `kv_connector_extra_config`：池化的其他可配置参数"

msgid ""
"To guarantee uniform hash generation, it is required to synchronize the "
"PYTHONHASHSEED environment variable across all nodes upon enabling KV Pool."
msgstr "为保证统一的哈希生成，在启用KV池时，需要在所有节点上同步PYTHONHASHSEED环境变量。"

