msgid ""
"`eviction_high_watermark_ratio` determines the watermark where Mooncake Store will perform eviction, and `eviction_ratio` determines the portion of stored objects that would be evicted.\n"
"`default_kv_lease_ttl` controls the default lease TTL for KV objects (milliseconds); configure it via `--default_kv_lease_ttl` and keep it larger than `ASCEND_CONNECT_TIMEOUT` and `ASCEND_TRANSFER_TIMEOUT`."
msgstr ""
"`eviction_high_watermark_ratio` 决定 Mooncake Store 执行驱逐的水位线，`eviction_ratio` 决定被驱逐的存储对象比例。\n"
"`default_kv_lease_ttl` 控制 KV 对象的默认租约 TTL（毫秒）；通过 `--default_kv_lease_ttl` 配置，并确保其大于 `ASCEND_CONNECT_TIMEOUT` 和 `ASCEND_TRANSFER_TIMEOUT`。"

