"吞吐量进行调整。由于 `-w` 会消耗剩余的命令行参数，请将任何 `dscli start`\n"
"选项（如 `--timeout`）放在 `-w` 之前。"

msgid ""
"For more parameters, refer to the `dscli` usage documentation on the Yuanrong\n"
"Datasystem official site:\n"
"<https://atomgit.com/openeuler/yuanrong-datasystem>"
msgstr ""
