msgid "#### Remote H2D Requirements"
msgstr "#### 远程 H2D 要求"

msgid ""
"Set `DS_ENABLE_REMOTE_H2D=1` only when Remote Host-to-Device transfer is\n"
"enabled and verified in the Yuanrong Datasystem deployment:"
msgstr ""
"仅在元戎 Datasystem 部署中启用并验证了远程主机到设备传输时，才设置\n"
"`DS_ENABLE_REMOTE_H2D=1`："

msgid ""
"* Reserve enough 2 MiB HugeTLB pages before starting the worker. For 40 GiB\n"
"  shared memory, reserve at least 20480 2 MiB huge pages.\n"
"* Start each Datasystem worker with Remote H2D enabled. The worker start\n"
"  command must include `--remote_h2d_device_ids`, `--enable_huge_tlb true`,\n"
"  `--arena_per_tenant 1`, and `--enable_fallocate false`. Using multiple\n"
"  available NPU device IDs is recommended, for example `\"0,1,2,3,4,5,6,7\"` on\n"
"  an 8-NPU node."
msgstr ""
"* 在启动工作进程前预留足够的 2 MiB HugeTLB 页。对于 40 GiB\n"
"  共享内存，请预留至少 20480 个 2 MiB 大页。\n"
"* 以启用远程 H2D 的方式启动每个 Datasystem 工作进程。工作进程启动\n"
"  命令必须包含 `--remote_h2d_device_ids`、`--enable_huge_tlb true`、\n"
"  `--arena_per_tenant 1` 和 `--enable_fallocate false`。建议使用多个\n"
"  可用的 NPU 设备 ID，例如在 8-NPU 节点上使用 `\"0,1,2,3,4,5,6,7\"`。"

msgid ""
"* Make sure the NPU driver, firmware, and CANN toolkit required by Yuanrong\n"
"  Remote H2D are installed and visible to the worker process. In containers,\n"
"  mount the Ascend driver path, `npu-smi`, `hccn_tool`, `/etc/hccn.conf`,\n"
"  `/etc/ascend_install.info`, and the required `/dev/davinci*` devices.\n"
"* Verify the NPU and RoCE environment before enabling the client flag:"
msgstr ""
"* 确保元戎远程 H2D 所需的 NPU 驱动、固件和 CANN 工具包已安装且对工作进程可见。在容器中，\n"
"  挂载 Ascend 驱动路径、`npu-smi`、`hccn_tool`、`/etc/hccn.conf`、\n"
"  `/etc/ascend_install.info` 以及所需的 `/dev/davinci*` 设备。\n"
"* 在启用客户端标志前验证 NPU 和 RoCE 环境："

msgid ""
"If these checks fail, keep `DS_ENABLE_REMOTE_H2D=0` and use the default\n"
"Datasystem transfer path."
msgstr ""
"如果这些检查失败，请保持 `DS_ENABLE_REMOTE_H2D=0` 并使用默认的\n"
"Datasystem 传输路径。"

msgid "### Run AscendStoreConnector with Yuanrong backend"
msgstr "### 使用元戎后端运行 AscendStoreConnector"

msgid "Use `AscendStoreConnector` with `backend: \"yuanrong\"`:"
msgstr "使用 `AscendStoreConnector` 并设置 `backend: \"yuanrong\"`："

msgid ""
"`lookup_rpc_port` is the RPC port used between the pooling scheduler process\n"
"and the worker process. Each instance must use a unique port value."
msgstr ""
"`lookup_rpc_port` 是池化调度进程与工作进程之间使用的 RPC 端口。\n"
"每个实例必须使用唯一的端口值。"

msgid "### Notes"
msgstr "### 注意事项"

msgid ""
"* The Yuanrong backend normalizes KV keys before calling Datasystem. Supported\n"
"  ASCII keys up to 1024 bytes are preserved. Longer keys or keys containing\n"
"  unsupported characters are rewritten to a maximum of 1024 characters with a\n"
"  hash suffix, so do not rely on the raw key string when debugging backend\n"
"  storage.\n"
"* No extra buffer pre-registration step is required for Yuanrong. The backend\n"
"  uses device pointers directly when building blob lists."
msgstr ""
"* 元戎后端在调用 Datasystem 之前会对 KV 键进行规范化。支持的最长 1024 字节的\n"
"  ASCII 键会被保留。更长的键或包含不支持字符的键会被重写为最多 1024 个字符并附加\n"
"  哈希后缀，因此在调试后端存储时不要依赖原始键字符串。\n"
"* 元戎不需要额外的缓冲区预注册步骤。后端在构建 blob 列表时直接使用设备指针。"

msgid "## FAQ"
msgstr "## 常见问题"

msgid "### 1. Mooncake FAQ"
msgstr "### 1. Mooncake 常见问题"

msgid "#### 1.1 failed to put/get key"
msgstr "#### 1.1 放置/获取键失败"

msgid ""
"When vLLM reports failed `put` or `get` operations, first check whether the "
"error is reported by Mooncake itself."
msgstr "当 vLLM 报告 `put` 或 `get` 操作失败时，首先检查该错误是否由 Mooncake 自身报告。"

msgid ""
"* If the error is reported by Mooncake:\n"
"    * For `put` failures, check whether the Mooncake log contains `NO_AVAILABLE_HANDLE` or `BatchPut failed ... due to insufficient space`. This usually means the remaining space after eviction is not enough for one `BatchPut` request. Ensure the space left by the eviction policy (for example, the capacity implied by `1 - eviction_ratio`) can hold one batch put, or consider increasing the available capacity, increasing eviction headroom, or reducing the batch size.\n"
"    * For `get` failures, check whether the Mooncake log contains `lease_expired_before_data_transfer_completed key=...` or returns `LEASE_EXPIRED`. This means the KV object lease expired before the data transfer completed. Increase `--default_kv_lease_ttl` for `mooncake_master` as needed, and keep it larger than `ASCEND_CONNECT_TIMEOUT` and `ASCEND_TRANSFER_TIMEOUT`.\n"
"* If the error is not reported by Mooncake, it is likely an HIXL (ascend_direct) transfer-layer issue. Collect plog files under `/root/ascend/log/debug/plog` and check whether the issue matches a known HIXL problem."
msgstr ""
"* 如果错误由 Mooncake 报告：\n"
"    * 对于 `put` 失败，检查 Mooncake 日志是否包含 `NO_AVAILABLE_HANDLE` 或 `BatchPut failed ... due to insufficient space`。这通常意味着驱逐后剩余空间不足以容纳一个 `BatchPut` 请求。请确保驱逐策略留下的空间（例如，`1 - eviction_ratio` 隐含的容量）能够容纳一次批量 put，或者考虑增加可用容量、增加驱逐余量或减小批量大小。\n"
"    * 对于 `get` 失败，检查 Mooncake 日志是否包含 `lease_expired_before_data_transfer_completed key=...` 或返回 `LEASE_EXPIRED`。这意味着 KV 对象租约在数据传输完成前已过期。根据需要增加 `mooncake_master` 的 `--default_kv_lease_ttl`，并确保其大于 `ASCEND_CONNECT_TIMEOUT` 和 `ASCEND_TRANSFER_TIMEOUT`。\n"
"* 如果错误不是由 Mooncake 报告，则很可能是 HIXL (ascend_direct) 传输层问题。收集 `/root/ascend/log/debug/plog` 下的 plog 文件，并检查该问题是否与已知的 HIXL 问题匹配。"

msgid ""
"For common troubleshooting and issue localization guidance for HIXL (ascend_direct), see:\n"
"<https://gitcode.com/cann/hixl/wiki/HIXL%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E5%AE%9A%E4%BD%8D%E6%89%8B%E5%86%8C.md>"
msgstr ""
"有关 HIXL (ascend_direct) 的常见故障排除和问题定位指南，请参阅：\n"
"<https://gitcode.com/cann/hixl/wiki/HIXL%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E5%AE%9A%E4%BD%8D%E6%89%8B%E5%86%8C.md>"

msgid "#### 1.2 SSD FAQ"
msgstr "#### 1.2 SSD 常见问题"

msgid "##### 1.2.1 SEGMENT_NOT_FOUND with SSD offload"
msgstr "##### 1.2.1 SSD 卸载时的 SEGMENT_NOT_FOUND"

msgid ""
"If client logs show `OffloadObjectHeartbeat failed, error code is "
"SEGMENT_NOT_FOUND`, Master has unmounted the rank's `LOCAL_DISK` segment "
"(usually after `client_expired` when Ping stops refreshing TTL). SSD offload"
" on that rank stops until the segment is registered again."
msgstr ""
"如果客户端日志显示 `OffloadObjectHeartbeat failed, error code is SEGMENT_NOT_FOUND`，则"
" Master 已卸载该 rank 的 `LOCAL_DISK` 段（通常在 Ping 停止刷新 TTL 导致 `client_expired` "
"之后）。该 rank 上的 SSD 卸载将停止，直到该段被重新注册。"

msgid ""
"**Typical trigger (with `enable_cpu_binding=true`):** Mooncake starts Ping "
"during init, then vLLM-Ascend `bind_cpus()` runs `migratepages`/IRQ binding;"
" the Ping thread is not pinned and can miss beats under the default "
"`client_ttl=10`."
msgstr ""
"**典型触发条件（当 `enable_cpu_binding=true` 时）：** Mooncake 在初始化期间启动 Ping，然后 vLLM-"
"Ascend 的 `bind_cpus()` 运行 `migratepages`/IRQ 绑定；Ping 线程未被绑定，因此在默认 "
"`client_ttl=10` 下可能会错过心跳。"

msgid ""
"Also restart Master together with vLLM to avoid stale "
"`segment_already_exists` state when debugging restarts."
msgstr "同时重启 Master 和 vLLM，以避免在调试重启时出现陈旧的 `segment_already_exists` 状态。"

msgid ""
"##### 1.2.2 Fabric memory size alignment (A3 + "
"`ASCEND_ENABLE_USE_FABRIC_MEM=1`)"
msgstr "##### 1.2.2 Fabric 内存大小对齐 (A3 + `ASCEND_ENABLE_USE_FABRIC_MEM=1`)"

msgid ""
"On A3 with fabric memory enabled, **each** fabric mem allocation must be an "
"integer multiple of **1 GB** (1073741824 bytes). Mooncake does not round "
"sizes up automatically."
msgstr ""
"在启用了 fabric 内存的 A3 上，**每次** fabric 内存分配必须是 **1 GB**（1073741824 "
"字节）的整数倍。Mooncake 不会自动向上取整大小。"

msgid ""
"`local_buffer_size` in `mooncake.json` is **not** used under fabric mem "
"(vLLM-Ascend passes `0` to `setup()`)."
msgstr ""
"`mooncake.json` 中的 `local_buffer_size` 在 fabric 内存模式下**不**使用（vLLM-Ascend 向 "
"`setup()` 传递 `0`）。"

msgid ""
"**Risk if misaligned:** `adxl MallocMem` / `aclrtMapMem` fails with "
"`Invalid_Argument`. With SSD offload enabled, a failed "
"`MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_LOCAL_BUFFER_SIZE_BYTES` allocation can segfault during "
"`FileStorage` init and abort vLLM startup. Avoid values such as "
"`\"1280MB\"`, `\"512MB\"`, or `\"1.5GB\"`."
msgstr ""
"**未对齐的风险：** `adxl MallocMem` / `aclrtMapMem` 失败并返回 `Invalid_Argument`。启用 SSD"
" 卸载后，`MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_LOCAL_BUFFER_SIZE_BYTES` 分配失败可能导致 `FileStorage` "
"初始化期间出现段错误并中止 vLLM 启动。避免使用诸如 `\"1280MB\"`、`\"512MB\"` 或 `\"1.5GB\"` 之类的值。"

msgid ""
"**Fabric mem quota:** Both `global_segment_size` and "
"`MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_LOCAL_BUFFER_SIZE_BYTES` are separate fabric mem "
"allocations **per rank**. Their sizes add up against the HIXL fabric mem "
"limit configured via `ASCEND_GLOBAL_RESOURCE_CONFIG` (e.g. "
"`\"fabric_memory.max_capacity\":32`, unit GB per process — see HIXL docs). "
"Rough budget per rank:"
msgstr ""
"**Fabric 内存配额：** `global_segment_size` 和 "
"`MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_LOCAL_BUFFER_SIZE_BYTES` 都是**每个 rank** 独立的 fabric "
"内存分配。它们的大小累加后受限于通过 `ASCEND_GLOBAL_RESOURCE_CONFIG` 配置的 HIXL fabric 内存限制（例如 "
"`\"fabric_memory.max_capacity\":32`，单位 GB/进程 — 请参阅 HIXL 文档）。每个 rank 的大致预算："

msgid ""
"**Risk if quota is too low:** Some ranks fail with "
"`Memory_Allocation_Failure(EL0004)` after `global_segment_size` succeeds but"
" `MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_LOCAL_BUFFER_SIZE_BYTES` allocation fails. Increase "
"`fabric_memory.max_capacity`, reduce `global_segment_size` or "
"`MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_LOCAL_BUFFER_SIZE_BYTES`, or ensure the node has enough "
"host memory."
msgstr ""
"**配额过低的風險：** 某些 rank 在 `global_segment_size` 成功但 "
"`MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_LOCAL_BUFFER_SIZE_BYTES` 分配失败时，会报错 "
"`Memory_Allocation_Failure(EL0004)`。请增加 `fabric_memory.max_capacity`，减小 "
"`global_segment_size` 或 "
"`MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_LOCAL_BUFFER_SIZE_BYTES`，或确保节点有足够的主机内存。"

msgid "Example (add to your vLLM startup script when SSD offload is on):"
msgstr "示例（在 SSD 卸载开启时，添加到您的 vLLM 启动脚本中）："

msgid "**set ASCEND_GLOBAL_RESOURCE_CONFIG only if fabric mem is too low.**"
msgstr "**仅在 fabric 内存过低时设置 ASCEND_GLOBAL_RESOURCE_CONFIG。**"

msgid "##### 1.2.3 Sizing MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_LOCAL_BUFFER_SIZE_BYTES"
msgstr "##### 1.2.3 调整 MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_LOCAL_BUFFER_SIZE_BYTES 大小"

msgid ""
"When `enable_ssd_offload=true`, Mooncake allocates a **separate per-rank SSD"
" read/write buffer** sized by `MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_LOCAL_BUFFER_SIZE_BYTES`. "
"This buffer is **independent** of `global_segment_size` in `mooncake.json` —"
" increasing the segment does **not** fix `BUFFER_OVERFLOW` caused by an "
"undersized `MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_LOCAL_BUFFER_SIZE_BYTES`."
msgstr ""
"当 `enable_ssd_offload=true` 时，Mooncake 会分配一个**独立的、每个 rank 的 SSD "
"读/写缓冲区**，其大小由 `MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_LOCAL_BUFFER_SIZE_BYTES` 决定。此缓冲区**独立于** "
"`mooncake.json` 中的 `global_segment_size` — 增加段大小并**不能**解决由 "
"`MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_LOCAL_BUFFER_SIZE_BYTES` 过小导致的 `BUFFER_OVERFLOW` 问题。"

msgid ""
"If the buffer is too small, SSD reads fail with `BUFFER_OVERFLOW` "
"(`error_code=-10`) during `FileStorage::AllocateBatch`, and vLLM may fail "
"when `kv_load_failure_policy=fail`."
msgstr ""
"如果缓冲区太小，SSD 读取会在 `FileStorage::AllocateBatch` 期间失败并返回 `BUFFER_OVERFLOW` "
"(`error_code=-10`)，并且当 `kv_load_failure_policy=fail` 时，vLLM 可能会失败。"

msgid ""
"If you encounter `BUFFER_OVERFLOW` during use, try increasing "
"`MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_LOCAL_BUFFER_SIZE_BYTES`. Do not set it higher than the "
"**Available KV cache memory** value shown in vLLM worker logs:"
msgstr ""
"如果在使用过程中遇到 `BUFFER_OVERFLOW`，请尝试增大 "
"`MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_LOCAL_BUFFER_SIZE_BYTES`。不要将其设置为高于 vLLM 工作进程日志中显示的 **可用 KV"
" 缓存内存** 值："

msgid "Example:"
msgstr "示例："

msgid ""
"Use **byte literals only** (`10737418240`). `10G` / `10GB` are ignored and "
"fall back to the 1280 MB default."
msgstr "请**仅使用字节字面量**（`10737418240`）。`10G` / `10GB` 将被忽略并回退到 1280 MB 的默认值。"

msgid ""
"<details>\n"
"<summary>Notes</summary>"
msgstr ""
"<details>\n"
"<summary>说明</summary>"

msgid ""
"* `--max-num-batched-tokens` only chunks prefill compute; it does **not** "
"reduce the memory required by `MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_LOCAL_BUFFER_SIZE_BYTES`."
msgstr ""
"* `--max-num-batched-tokens` 仅对预填充计算进行分块；它**不会**减少 "
"`MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_LOCAL_BUFFER_SIZE_BYTES` 所需的内存。"

msgid "</details>"
msgstr "</details>"

msgid "###### Host memory budget (single node)"
msgstr "###### 主机内存预算（单节点）"

msgid ""
"`MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_LOCAL_BUFFER_SIZE_BYTES` is allocated **per rank**, in "
"addition to `global_segment_size`:"
msgstr ""
"`MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_LOCAL_BUFFER_SIZE_BYTES` 是**按 rank** 分配的，除此之外还有 "
"`global_segment_size`："

msgid ""
"Ensure `free -h` **available** on the host exceeds this sum plus vLLM "
"overhead. `MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_LOCAL_BUFFER_SIZE_BYTES` does **not** need to "
"fit inside `global_segment_size`."
msgstr ""
"确保主机上 `free -h` 的**可用**内存超过此总和加上 vLLM "
"的开销。`MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_LOCAL_BUFFER_SIZE_BYTES` **不需要** 适应 "
"`global_segment_size`。"

msgid "###### Verify after tuning"
msgstr "###### 调优后验证"

msgid ""
"1. Startup: each rank logs `AlignedClientBufferAllocator: allocated <N> bytes` with your configured size.\n"
"2. Under load: no `BUFFER_OVERFLOW` / `Failed to get ... keys out of ... error_codes=[-10]`.\n"
"3. If failures persist with a large buffer, check overlapping loads (`load_async`)."
msgstr ""
"1. 启动时：每个 rank 会记录 `AlignedClientBufferAllocator: allocated <N> bytes`，其中包含您配置的大小。\n"
"2. 负载下：没有 `BUFFER_OVERFLOW` / `Failed to get ... keys out of ... error_codes=[-10]`。\n"
"3. 如果使用大缓冲区时故障仍然存在，请检查重叠加载（`load_async`）。"

