msgid ""
"| `consumer_is_to_load` | Whether Decode node load KV cache from KV Pool. "
"The default value is false. |"
msgstr "| `consumer_is_to_load` | Decode节点是否从KV Pool加载KV cache。默认值为false。 |"

msgid ""
"| `prefill_pp_size` | Prefill PP size, needs to be set when Prefill node "
"enables PP. |"
msgstr "| `prefill_pp_size` | Prefill PP大小，当Prefill节点启用PP时需要设置。 |"

msgid ""
"| `prefill_pp_layer_partition` | Prefill PP layer partition, needs to be set"
" when Prefill node enables PP. |"
msgstr "| `prefill_pp_layer_partition` | Prefill PP层分区，当Prefill节点启用PP时需要设置。 |"

msgid ""
"| 800 I/T A3 series | HDK >= 26.0<br>or HDK >= 25.5 with mooncake >= "
"v0.3.11<br>CANN >= 9.0.0<br>LingQu Computing Network >= 1.5 | `export "
"ASCEND_ENABLE_USE_FABRIC_MEM=1` | **Recommended**. Enables unified memory "
"address direct transmission scheme. With SSD offload, see [Fabric memory "
"size alignment](#122-fabric-memory-size-alignment-a3--"
"ascend_enable_use_fabric_mem1) — memory sizes must be aligned to 1GB. |"
msgstr ""
"| 800 I/T A3系列 | HDK >= 26.0<br>或 HDK >= 25.5 且 mooncake >= v0.3.11<br>CANN "
">= 9.0.0<br>灵衢计算网络 >= 1.5 | `export ASCEND_ENABLE_USE_FABRIC_MEM=1` | "
"**推荐**。启用统一内存地址直传方案。使用SSD卸载时，请参见[Fabric内存大小对齐](#122-fabric-memory-size-"
"alignment-a3--ascend_enable_use_fabric_mem1) — 内存大小必须按1GB对齐。 |"

msgid ""
"| 800 I/T A3 series | If any dependency above is not met | `export "
"ASCEND_BUFFER_POOL=4:8` | Configures the number and size of buffers on the "
"NPU Device for aggregation and KV transfer (e.g., `4:8` means 4 buffers of "
"8MB). |"
msgstr ""
"| 800 I/T A3系列 | 如果上述任一依赖不满足 | `export ASCEND_BUFFER_POOL=4:8` | "
"配置NPU设备上用于聚合和KV传输的缓冲区数量和大小（例如，`4:8`表示4个8MB的缓冲区）。 |"

msgid ""
"| 800 I/T A2 series | HDK >= 25.5 is recommended | `export "
"HCCL_INTRA_ROCE_ENABLE=1` | Required by direct transmission scheme on 800 "
"I/T A2 series|"
msgstr ""
"| 800 I/T A2系列 | 建议HDK >= 25.5 | `export HCCL_INTRA_ROCE_ENABLE=1` | 800 I/T"
" A2系列直传方案所需 |"

msgid ""
"| `enable_offload` | Set to `true` to enable SSD offload in Mooncake master."
" Keep the master port aligned with `master_server_address` in "
"`mooncake.json`. |"
msgstr ""
"| `enable_offload` | 设置为`true`以在Mooncake "
"master中启用SSD卸载。保持master端口与`mooncake.json`中的`master_server_address`一致。 |"

msgid ""
"| `client_ttl` | Seconds a client stays alive after the last Ping. CLI "
"default is `10`; see [SEGMENT_NOT_FOUND with SSD "
"offload](#121-segment_not_found-with-ssd-offload). |"
msgstr ""
"| `client_ttl` | "
"客户端在最后一次Ping后保持存活的秒数。CLI默认值为`10`；请参见[SSD卸载时的SEGMENT_NOT_FOUND](#121-segment_not_found-"
"with-ssd-offload)。 |"

msgid ""
"| `enable_ssd_offload` | Set to `true` to enable SSD offload. Environment "
"variables are not supported. |"
msgstr "| `enable_ssd_offload` | 设置为`true`以启用SSD卸载。不支持环境变量。 |"

msgid ""
"| `ssd_offload_path` | **Required when `enable_ssd_offload` is `true`.** "
"Absolute path to a local directory where Mooncake stores offloaded KV data "
"(for example, `/nvme/mooncake_offload`). The directory must exist and be "
"writable by the vLLM process; create it before startup (`mkdir -p <path>`). "
"Relative paths, symbolic links, and paths containing `..` are rejected by "
"Mooncake. Passed to `MooncakeDistributedStore.setup()` as the SSD storage "
"root (equivalent to `MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_FILE_STORAGE_PATH` in standalone "
"clients). Configure this field in `mooncake.json` only; environment "
"variables are not supported. |"
msgstr ""
"| `ssd_offload_path` | **当`enable_ssd_offload`为`true`时必需。** "
"Mooncake存储卸载的KV数据的本地目录的绝对路径（例如，`/nvme/mooncake_offload`）。该目录必须存在且可由vLLM进程写入；请在启动前创建它（`mkdir"
" -p "
"<path>`）。Mooncake拒绝相对路径、符号链接以及包含`..`的路径。作为SSD存储根目录传递给`MooncakeDistributedStore.setup()`（相当于独立客户端中的`MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_FILE_STORAGE_PATH`）。仅在`mooncake.json`中配置此字段；不支持环境变量。"
" |"

msgid ""
"| `MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_LOCAL_BUFFER_SIZE_BYTES` | `1342177280` (1280 MB) | Per-"
"rank SSD read/write buffer size in bytes. **Not** configurable in "
"`mooncake.json`. If you hit `BUFFER_OVERFLOW`, increase this value — see "
"[Sizing MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_LOCAL_BUFFER_SIZE_BYTES](#123-sizing-"
"mooncake_offload_local_buffer_size_bytes). **On A3 with "
"`ASCEND_ENABLE_USE_FABRIC_MEM=1`, must be aligned to 1GB and counts toward "
"per-rank fabric mem quota (see [Fabric memory size alignment](#122-fabric-"
"memory-size-alignment-a3--ascend_enable_use_fabric_mem1))**. |"
msgstr ""
"| `MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_LOCAL_BUFFER_SIZE_BYTES` | `1342177280` (1280 MB) | "
"每个rank的SSD读写缓冲区大小（字节）。**不可**在`mooncake.json`中配置。如果遇到`BUFFER_OVERFLOW`，请增大此值——请参见[调整MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_LOCAL_BUFFER_SIZE_BYTES的大小](#123-sizing-"
"mooncake_offload_local_buffer_size_bytes)。**在A3上使用`ASCEND_ENABLE_USE_FABRIC_MEM=1`时，必须按1GB对齐，并计入每个rank的fabric"
" mem配额（请参见[Fabric内存大小对齐](#122-fabric-memory-size-alignment-a3--"
"ascend_enable_use_fabric_mem1)）。** |"

msgid ""
"| `MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_BUCKET_MAX_TOTAL_SIZE` | `0` | Eviction threshold in "
"bytes. When set to `0`, the backend uses **90% of the physical disk "
"capacity** as the quota. Set an explicit value to control disk usage "
"precisely. |"
msgstr ""
"| `MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_BUCKET_MAX_TOTAL_SIZE` | `0` | "
"逐出阈值（字节）。当设置为`0`时，后端使用**物理磁盘容量的90%**作为配额。设置显式值以精确控制磁盘使用量。 |"

msgid ""
"| `MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_BUCKET_EVICTION_POLICY` | `none` | Eviction policy: "
"`none` (writes fail when full), `fifo`, or `lru`. |"
msgstr ""
"| `MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_BUCKET_EVICTION_POLICY` | `none` | "
"逐出策略：`none`（满时写入失败）、`fifo`或`lru`。 |"

msgid ""
"| `MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_TOTAL_SIZE_LIMIT_BYTES` | `2199023255552` (2 TB) | "
"**Per-rank** maximum disk usage reported to Mooncake master. Master "
"aggregates this across clients (roughly **2 TB × rank count** in the `SSD "
"Storage` total). **Always override** to match real disk capacity — the "
"default often exceeds available space. |"
msgstr ""
"| `MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_TOTAL_SIZE_LIMIT_BYTES` | `2199023255552` (2 TB) | "
"报告给Mooncake master的**每个rank**的最大磁盘使用量。Master跨客户端聚合此值（在`SSD Storage`总计中约为**2 "
"TB × rank数量**）。**始终覆盖**以匹配实际磁盘容量——默认值通常超过可用空间。 |"

msgid ""
"| `ock.mmc.meta_service_url` | Configure the IP address and port number of "
"the master node. The IP address and port number of the P node and D node can"
" be the same. |"
msgstr ""
"| `ock.mmc.meta_service_url` | 配置master节点的IP地址和端口号。P节点和D节点的IP地址和端口号可以相同。 |"

msgid ""
"| `ock.mmc.local_service.config_store_url` | Configure the IP address and "
"port number of the master node. The IP address and port number of the P node"
" and D node can be the same. |"
msgstr ""
"| `ock.mmc.local_service.config_store_url` | "
"配置master节点的IP地址和端口号。P节点和D节点的IP地址和端口号可以相同。 |"

msgid ""
"| `ock.mmc.local_service.world_size` | Total count of local service, "
"including services that will be added in the future. |"
msgstr "| `ock.mmc.local_service.world_size` | 本地服务的总数，包括将来会添加的服务。 |"

msgid ""
"| `ock.mmc.local_service.protocol` | `device_rdma` (supported for A2 and A3 "
"when device ROCE available, recommended for A2), `device_sdma` (supported "
"for A3 when HCCS available, recommended for A3). Currently does not support "
"heterogeneous protocol setting.|"
msgstr ""
"| `ock.mmc.local_service.protocol` | "
"`device_rdma`（当设备ROCE可用时，A2和A3支持，推荐用于A2），`device_sdma`（当HCCS可用时，A3支持，推荐用于A3）。当前不支持异构协议设置。|"

msgid ""
"| `ock.mmc.local_service.dram.size` | Sets the size of the memory occupied "
"by the master. The configured value is the size of the memory occupied by "
"each card. |"
msgstr ""
"| `ock.mmc.local_service.dram.size` | 设置master占用的内存大小。配置的值是每张卡占用的内存大小。 |"

msgid ""
"| `log_dir` | Sets the Datasystem worker log directory. Create the directory"
" and grant the worker process write permission before startup. |"
msgstr "| `log_dir` | 设置Datasystem工作进程日志目录。启动前创建该目录并授予工作进程写入权限。 |"

msgid ""
"| `arena_per_tenant=1` | Uses one shared-memory arena per tenant as a "
"conservative starting point for memory and file-descriptor usage. |"
msgstr "| `arena_per_tenant=1` | 每个租户使用一个共享内存区域，作为内存和文件描述符使用的保守起点。 |"

msgid ""
"| `enable_huge_tlb=true` | Backs worker shared memory with HugeTLB pages. "
"Reserve enough 2 MiB huge pages before starting the worker. |"
msgstr ""
"| `enable_huge_tlb=true` | 使用HugeTLB页面支持工作进程共享内存。在启动工作进程前预留足够的2 MiB大页。 |"

msgid ""
"| `enable_fallocate=false` | Disables `fallocate` for the shared-memory "
"file; use this setting with the HugeTLB configuration above. |"
msgstr ""
"| `enable_fallocate=false` | 禁用共享内存文件的`fallocate`；将此设置与上述HugeTLB配置一起使用。 |"

msgid "| `rpc_thread_num=64` | Sets the RPC/ZMQ service concurrency. |"
msgstr "| `rpc_thread_num=64` | 设置RPC/ZMQ服务的并发数。 |"

msgid ""
"| `oc_thread_num=64` | Sets the Object Cache business-thread pool size. |"
msgstr "| `oc_thread_num=64` | 设置对象缓存业务线程池大小。 |"

msgid ""
"| `enable_worker_worker_batch_get=true` | Enables batched Object Cache reads"
" between Datasystem workers. |"
msgstr ""
"| `enable_worker_worker_batch_get=true` | 启用 Datasystem 工作节点之间的批量对象缓存读取。 |"

msgid ""
"| `sc_regular_socket_num=0`, `sc_stream_socket_num=0` | Disables the Stream "
"Cache service. Both values must be greater than zero to enable it; keep them"
" at zero when KV Pool does not use Stream Cache. |"
msgstr ""
"| `sc_regular_socket_num=0`, `sc_stream_socket_num=0` | "
"禁用流缓存服务。两个值都必须大于零才能启用；当 KV Pool 不使用流缓存时，请将其保持为零。 |"

msgid ""
"| `PYTHONHASHSEED` | Yes | `0` | Must be consistent across all nodes to "
"guarantee uniform hash generation. |"
msgstr "| `PYTHONHASHSEED` | 是 | `0` | 所有节点必须保持一致，以确保生成统一的哈希值。 |"

msgid ""
"| `DS_WORKER_ADDR` | Yes | N/A | Datasystem worker address in "
"`<host>:<port>` format. This must match the local `dscli start "
"--worker_address` value. |"
msgstr ""
"| `DS_WORKER_ADDR` | 是 | 不适用 | Datasystem 工作节点地址，格式为 `<host>:<port>`。此值必须与本地"
" `dscli start --worker_address` 的值一致。 |"

msgid ""
"| `DATASYSTEM_CLIENT_LOG_DIR` | No | `~/.datasystem/logs` | Directory for "
"Yuanrong client SDK logs created by the vLLM process. Use a directory "
"separate from the worker logs. |"
msgstr ""
"| `DATASYSTEM_CLIENT_LOG_DIR` | 否 | `~/.datasystem/logs` | vLLM 进程创建的元融客户端 "
"SDK 日志目录。请使用与工作节点日志不同的目录。 |"

msgid ""
"| `DS_ENABLE_EXCLUSIVE_CONNECTION` | No | `0` | Passed to Yuanrong "
"`HeteroClient.enable_exclusive_connection`. Use `1` to enable the exclusive "
"connection mode when required by your deployment. |"
msgstr ""
"| `DS_ENABLE_EXCLUSIVE_CONNECTION` | 否 | `0` | 传递给元融 "
"`HeteroClient.enable_exclusive_connection`。当部署需要时，使用 `1` 启用独占连接模式。 |"

msgid ""
"| `DS_ENABLE_REMOTE_H2D` | No | `0` | Passed to Yuanrong "
"`HeteroClient.enable_remote_h2d`. Use `1` only after the Remote H2D "
"requirements below are met. |"
msgstr ""
"| `DS_ENABLE_REMOTE_H2D` | 否 | `0` | 传递给元融 "
"`HeteroClient.enable_remote_h2d`。仅在满足以下远程 H2D 要求后使用 `1`。 |"

msgid ""
"| **Temporary:** raise Master TTL | e.g. `mooncake_master ... "
"--client_ttl=120`. Tune to your init/warmup window (often `60`–`120` is "
"enough). Does not fix the root cause. |"
msgstr ""
"| **临时方案：** 提高 Master TTL | 例如 `mooncake_master ... "
"--client_ttl=120`。根据您的初始化/预热窗口进行调整（通常 `60`–`120` 就足够了）。不能解决根本原因。 |"

msgid ""
"| **Recovery:** upgrade Mooncake | Versions **> v0.3.11** (main branch) can "
"remount `LOCAL_DISK` and rescan metadata after `SEGMENT_NOT_FOUND`. This "
"**recovers after** cleanup; it does **not** prevent expiry or in-flight "
"request failures while metadata is gone. |"
msgstr ""
"| **恢复方案：** 升级 Mooncake | **> v0.3.11** 版本（主分支）可以在 `SEGMENT_NOT_FOUND` 后重新挂载"
" `LOCAL_DISK` 并重新扫描元数据。这可以在清理后**恢复**；但不能防止元数据丢失期间的过期或正在处理的请求失败。 |"

msgid ""
"| **Root fix:** Mooncake Ping CPU affinity | Pin the storage Ping thread to "
"a release/isolated CPU (Mooncake-side change). Optional vLLM-Ascend "
"cooperation to pass the release CPU per rank. |"
msgstr ""
"| **根本修复：** Mooncake Ping CPU 亲和性 | 将存储 Ping 线程绑定到一个释放/隔离的 CPU（Mooncake "
"侧更改）。可选地，vLLM-Ascend 协作以传递每个 rank 的释放 CPU。 |"

msgid ""
"| `global_segment_size` | `mooncake.json` or export "
"`MOONCAKE_GLOBAL_SEGMENT_SIZE` | Each rank's segment size must be aligned to"
" 1GB (e.g. `\"1GB\"`, `\"20GB\"`). |"
msgstr ""
"| `global_segment_size` | `mooncake.json` 或导出 `MOONCAKE_GLOBAL_SEGMENT_SIZE`"
" | 每个 rank 的段大小必须与 1GB 对齐（例如 `\"1GB\"`、`\"20GB\"`）。 |"

msgid ""
"| `MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_LOCAL_BUFFER_SIZE_BYTES` | export "
"`MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_LOCAL_BUFFER_SIZE_BYTES` (only when "
"`enable_ssd_offload=true`) | Must be aligned to 1GB. Default is 1280 MB "
"(1.25 GB), which is **not** aligned and is too small for long-context SSD "
"loads — size with [Sizing "
"MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_LOCAL_BUFFER_SIZE_BYTES](#123-sizing-"
"mooncake_offload_local_buffer_size_bytes). |"
msgstr ""
"| `MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_LOCAL_BUFFER_SIZE_BYTES` | 导出 "
"`MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_LOCAL_BUFFER_SIZE_BYTES`（仅在 `enable_ssd_offload=true` 时） |"
" 必须与 1GB 对齐。默认值为 1280 MB（1.25 GB），该值**未**对齐，且对于长上下文 SSD 负载来说太小——请根据[调整 "
"MOONCAKE_OFFLOAD_LOCAL_BUFFER_SIZE_BYTES 大小](#123-sizing-"
"mooncake_offload_local_buffer_size_bytes)进行设置。 |"
